org.webcurator.core.permissionmapping
Class MappingView

java.lang.Object
  org.webcurator.core.permissionmapping.MappingView

public class MappingView
extends java.lang.Object

The MappingView class records mappings between UrlPatterns and Permissions based on effective base domains. The goal is to provide fast lookups for the HierarchicalPermissionMappingStrategy.

Author:
bbeaumont
